# Technology Stack & Architecture

## Frontend Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 13 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- **State Management**: Zustand
- **Platform**: PWA (Progressive Web App) first, native later

## Backend Stack
- **Edge Runtime**: Cloudflare Workers
- **AI Processing**: Python 3.12 + LangGraph 0.9 + FastAPI
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 16 Serverless (Neon/Supabase)
- **Vector DB**: Pinecone Serverless v3
- **Analytics**: ClickHouse Cloud

## AI Generation Stack
- **LLM**: Claude-3 / Gemini
- **Image Generation**: Stable Diffusion XL (InvokeAI)
- **Voice Synthesis**: ElevenLabs Professional API
- **GPU Infrastructure**: Modal (spot instances for cost optimization)

## Infrastructure
- **Storage**: Cloudflare R2 + CDN
- **Authentication**: Supabase Auth (Magic Link)
- **Payment**: Stripe (Web) â†’ Paddle (international VAT)
- **Deployment**: Vercel (Frontend) + Cloudflare (Backend)

## Architecture Principles
- **Edge-first**: Low latency content delivery
- **Cost optimization**: Batch processing and caching
- **Scalability**: Serverless architecture
- **Security**: Data encryption and privacy compliance
